name: Techno-Cultural Evolution @acesun07 @neroone__
description: What does the future of NFT culture look like? As a protopian, it would be better if I don't speculate too much about the future but instead, look back at the progress of the past civilizations. My views on socio-cultural evolutions are about daily incremental progress, focusing on the here and now. The visual was done by neroone__ , and ideate by me. I'm posting on behalf of NFXT Collective. @nfxt_io #malaysianft
